{
  "stem": "20021.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as the years went by, later during Kristallnacht and so forth, you know, we heard over the radio more and more about Hitler and what's going to happen and what was happening in Germany.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Also, the German Jews of Polish extraction were expelled suddenly in 1938.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they arrived in our town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was committees organized to help them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we came in contact with them as a result of those committees.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I had some friends, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we heard stories from them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But of course, this was such a far cry from what happened later that nobody even remotely imagined that what later happened would happen, even though there was so much brutality during Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the subsequent expulsion of the Polish Jews was-- was-- just overnight he issued an edict.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And anybody-- anybody whose parents were born in Poland, he and his family, even the children were already born in Germany, were just thrown over the border, just like that.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And some of them came to Tarnow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Jews in Tarnow organized committees to help them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my parents were active in those committees.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And mostly, it was to find housing for them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we did find-- all of them, somehow we found accommodations for them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were supposed to befriend them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I befriended some boys, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father owned a factory which was making tar-paper and chemical products, mostly for the preservation of wood and things like that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was very busy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he was also very active in the community.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In particular, he was chairman of the board for the school which I went, and really was the biggest supporter of that school.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
